title: Wheat Crop Acreage for United Kingdom and Ireland
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1852-1938 (2)--Original Data, 1932-1939. This Series Covers The United Kingdom And Eire, Called The British Isles In Wheat Studies To 1934. After 1934 Computed By Adding United Kingdom To Eire. Source: Data For 1852-1885: Journal Of The Royal Agricultural Society Of England, Third Series, 1893, Vol. 4, P. 132. Data For 1886-1938: Food Research Institute, "Wheat Studies", April 1933, P. 268; December 1933, P. 122; December 1938, P. 239.

This NBER data series a01031a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
